    "HOME_1": "In the era of credit-based training becoming increasingly popular in universities, managing class activities through traditional methods is facing significant challenges, especially in terms of efficiency and accuracy. With the aim of modernizing the process, the \"Class Activity Management System\" was developed to streamline activities such as attendance tracking, notifications, document management, and automated reporting.",
